column4: Apple accuses Qualcomm of patent infringement in countersuit
column5: Apple Inc on Wednesday filed a countersuit against Qualcomm Inc  alleging that Qualcomm's Snapdragon mobile phone chips that power a wide variety of Android-based devices infringe on Apple's patents  the latest development in a long-running dispute.
